{"word":"G1908 - ἐπηρεάζω - epēreázō - ep-ay-reh-ad'-zo - Use despitefully","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπηρεάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>epēreázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ep-ay-reh-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Use despitefully"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிந்தி, தூஷி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to insult; to treat abusively, use despitefully; to revile"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and (probably) <b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x0301;</b> <b>areia</b> (<i>threats</i>); to <i>insult</i>, <i>slander:</i> - use despitefully, falsely accuse."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}